com.camerontec.catalys.application.marketdata

Interface IMarketDataMessage

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IDepthEntryUpdateMessage, IDepthFullUpdateMessage, ITopOfBookMessage
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractDepthFullUpdateMessage, AbstractMarketDataMessage, DepthDecoratorBase, DepthEntryIncrementalDecorator, DepthFullUpdateDecorator, DepthFullUpdateIncrementalDecorator, DepthFullUpdateSnapshotDecorator, MarketDataDecoratorBase, ReusableDepthEntryUpdateMessage, ReusableDepthFullUpdateMessage, ReusableDepthSnapshotMessage, ReusableMarketDataTopOfBookSnapshot, ReusableMarketDataTopOfBookUpdate, SetValueStoreMessage, TopOfBookIncrementalDecorator, TopOfBookSnapshotDecorator

    public interface IMarketDataMessage
    All market data messages support this interface.

    It provides a standard way of defining the instrument associated with the message.

      • setInstrumentUpdateInfo

        void setInstrumentUpdateInfo(IInstrumentUpdateInfo updateInfo)
        Set the instrument update info associated with this message.

        This holds information about the update request associated with this message as well as the instrument with which this message is associated.

        Parameters:
        updateInfo - Instrument update information associated with message.
